Title : Marcus Passage
Text : '''Marcus Passage''' is a stretch of saltwater on the [[British Columbia Coast|North Coast region]] of [[British Columbia]], [[Canada]], offshore from the mouth of the [[Skeena River]], south and west of [[Smith Island (British Columbia)|Smith Island]] and south of the City of [[Prince Rupert, British Columbia|Prince Rupert]].<ref>[http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/35730.html BC Names/GeoBC entry "Marcus Passage"]</ref>

